Key Match Events: Gelson Dala scored twice for Angola in the 38th and 42nd minutes.
Mabululu scored the third goal for Angola in the 66th minute.
Neblú received a yellow card in the 17th minute.
Lubeni Haukongo received a yellow card in the 40th minute.
Post-Match Reflections: Angola's victory secured their place in the Africa Cup of Nations quarter-finals.
